            "title": "尖沙咀傷人案｜女事主親述驚嚇過程 遭利刀追捅2分半鐘 獲內地男相助制服女疑犯",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9b0472f35d49f9a1e1cdb301c8cec3d1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051501464160921.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>尖沙咀周三發生的剪刀傷人案件，事主在社交平台分享事發經過，指自己無故被襲，幸得路人協助下制服疑犯。\n\n</p>\n<p>女事主在社交平台Threads 表示，周三（14日）她本來相約朋友食飯，並提前預約了餐廳。當她在地鐵站走出商場時，迎面有一名女子走近。她指該名女子在「冇任何動機同預兆，冇對到視線」的情況下「一腳踢埋嚟」，使她大腿立即瘀黑。\n\n</p>\n<p>該名女子直接離開，事主遂上前追問：「點解要踢我，我唔識你呀？」未料，女子突然從袋中拿出一把剪刀，並開始追著事主捅刺，整個過程長達兩分半鐘，事主身上有5處被捅傷了。她指，當時由於鞋帶鬆脫，她向附近吸煙區的三名男士求助，但經過20秒「掙扎」後，依然沒有人出手幫忙。幸好一名內地男子出現並上前幫助，成功將嫌疑人壓制住。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249129/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女事主左手受傷。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4adbe6603a80ebff4f505336ba265aed/2025-05/498540576_17877462753326685_4816538839212828060_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女事主左手受傷。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249128/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"左手上有兩處傷痕。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6b2330fec29366061adbfe353723e2ff/2025-05/498177316_17877462744326685_8898357410332674192_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        左手上有兩處傷痕。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249127/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女事主嘴脣受傷。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/26512396a392701bd0fa20fa50cb39db/2025-05/497930902_17877462774326685_1124097197073323740_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女事主嘴脣受傷。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249131/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女子被制服後一度坐在地上，雙手被鎖上手銬。  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/541ef9d9c7740225d8f6c4b62b4a2583/2025-05/AQMSujdmRdf_zdP6tqb8Tu47c2k-WH4ntmQANx24aDeAmNYKRPVBlix75TFrHTVSOBmGsIbC8HiKHCQtqNqWCkKK_mp4_snapshot_00_25_280_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女子被制服後一度坐在地上，雙手被鎖上手銬。  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249132/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女子被制服後一度坐在地上，雙手被鎖上手銬。  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6db792ead5b36deda0ade717d6fc4b3f/2025-05/AQMSujdmRdf_zdP6tqb8Tu47c2k-WH4ntmQANx24aDeAmNYKRPVBlix75TFrHTVSOBmGsIbC8HiKHCQtqNqWCkKK_mp4_snapshot_00_14_469_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女子被制服後一度坐在地上，雙手被鎖上手銬。  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>事主稱，兇徒被制服後，用流利普通話講：「放開我啊。」她趁機錄下了兇手的樣貌，並迅速報警求助。\n\n</p>\n<p>事後，事主得知這名女子已經襲擊過多名風格相似的女性，稱自己並無與人有任何情感糾紛或仇恨。她感謝男子及警察的幫助，並指分享事發現段時，她容貌未有打碼，令她造成二次傷害。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068982/即時-港聞-尖沙咀傷人案-女事主親述驚嚇過程-遭利刀追捅2分半鐘-獲內地男相助制服女疑犯",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-15 01:56:18",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "警大埔冚非法麻雀賭檔 拘捕男負責人及6賭客",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警大埔冚非法麻雀賭檔，拘捕男負責人及6賭客。警方圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4e7ae8eb56f09b3725d55eedde09aac1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051500414397811.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警大埔冚非法麻雀賭檔，拘捕男負責人及6賭客。警方圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>大埔警區特別職務隊人員經深入調查後，周三（14日）下午約5時半突擊搜查大埔富善街一單位，搗破一個懷疑非法賭檔。\n\n</p>\n<p>該單位內一名42歲姓張本地男負責人涉嫌「經營賭博場所」及「在賭博場所內賭博」被捕。單位內5名本地女子及一名本地男子，年齡介乎60至69歲，則涉嫌「在賭博場所內賭博」被捕。\n\n</p>\n<p>行動中，人員共檢獲兩張電動麻雀枱、4副麻雀賭具、一批家具及約四410元現金。\n\n</p>\n<p>該名42歲男負責人已被暫控一項「經營賭博場所」及「在賭博場所內賭博」罪，而另外三名被捕女子則已各被暫控一項「在賭博場所內賭博」罪，案件將於六月六日上午在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。其餘被捕人已獲准保釋候查，須於六月中旬向警方報到。\n\n</p>\n<p>根據香港法例一百四十八章《賭博條例》，「經營賭博場所」及「在賭博場所內賭博」屬嚴重罪行，前者一經定罪最高可判罰款五百萬元及監禁七年，後者一經定罪最高可判罰款三萬元及監禁九個月。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068980/即時-港聞-警大埔冚非法麻雀賭檔-拘捕男負責人及6賭客",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-15 01:06:32",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Tim@Dear Jane為老婆在紅館提前慶生  Tyson Yoshi萬人下跟未婚妻嘴咀  魏浚笙帶傷睇騷堅持繼續開工",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\" Dear Jane慶祝入行二十周年演唱會《DEAREST DEAR JANE LIVE 2025》今晚（14日）在紅館舉行尾場。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a4772c4f468353bd4ed46ce2dbb5fb2b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051500444453945.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"> Dear Jane慶祝入行二十周年演唱會《DEAREST DEAR JANE LIVE 2025》今晚（14日）在紅館舉行尾場。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>Dear Jane慶祝入行二十周年演唱會《DEAREST DEAR JANE LIVE 2025》今晚（14日）在紅館舉行尾場，謝寧、馬浚偉、Serrini及Tyson Yoshi及未婚妻Christy等也前來捧場，至於主音黃天翱（Tim）的老婆楊洛婷與一對子女亦有到場。早前拍戲頸部受傷的魏浚笙亦有到場睇騷，精神不俗的他頸上貼了兩塊大膠布，被問到傷勢時，戴著口罩的他表示「好返好多」，又謂沒因傷而停工，但電影就未開始補拍。\n\n</p><h2>Tyson錫完勁尷尬</h2>\n<p>Dear Jane於升降台現身唱出《浮床》，之後他們的舞台更升上10尺高，即時炒熱現場氣氛，Tim指「今晚玩爆個場」。低音結他手Jackal與鼓手Nice一起於升降台打鼓及唱出《友情歲月》，在Jackal唱出《草戒指》時與觀眾玩遊戲，被攝影機影住的人要嘴咀，而當影住Tyson Yoshi與Christy時，只見Tyson先是一臉尷尬，但他最後也有跟遊戲規則，在全場過萬名觀眾看著下與Christy嘴咀，惹來全場大叫，錫完後Tyson亦變得非常怕醜。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當影住Tyson Yoshi與Christy時，只見Tyson先是一臉尷尬，但他最後也有跟遊戲規則。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c014419a5c8c77cf85e129c2117d67af/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0002.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當影住Tyson Yoshi與Christy時，只見Tyson先是一臉尷尬，但他最後也有跟遊戲規則。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\" Dear Jane於升降台現身唱出《浮床》\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5fa2674d616e776563157bcec0afd04b/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0018.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n         Dear Jane於升降台現身唱出《浮床》\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"之後他們的舞台更升上10尺高。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/482e895dfed49601fc99761eeca08760/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0020.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        之後他們的舞台更升上10尺高。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"即時炒熱現場氣氛。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2fcd49742da384a55160c5504bc87074/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0023.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        即時炒熱現場氣氛。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Tim指「今晚玩爆個場」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/94142c929dbb8b34f8c6ce9a9aafedb3/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0025.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Tim指「今晚玩爆個場」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"台上台下都非常興奮。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0bddcf9f1bdd6deeae4381f8c88ff979/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0026.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        台上台下都非常興奮。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"低音結他手Jackal與鼓手Nice一起於升降台打鼓及唱出《友情歲月》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/628d327bb220c8b7c73055cc67664c30/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0030.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        低音結他手Jackal與鼓手Nice一起於升降台打鼓及唱出《友情歲月》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Tim也幫手打鼓。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/49d536eaf57ee338fb589a7b6ef477c9/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0031.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Tim也幫手打鼓。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Jackal唱出《草戒指》時與觀眾玩遊戲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4a286dc1f62a291242cad318d93d291e/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0032.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Jackal唱出《草戒指》時與觀眾玩遊戲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Tim全晚表演都非常投入。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7afc3a5fd8a128d2fb2245f9df775ac0/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0033.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Tim全晚表演都非常投入。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>Tim與兒子對彈結他</h2>\n<p>在Tim彈結他時，兒子Tristan也走出坐位與台上爸爸對彈，更彈得很落力，非常可愛。在唱出《經過一些秋與冬》時，現場影著該MV系列的男主角胡卓希，全場再次起哄。而Tim也在演唱會上畀驚喜老婆，他先感激對方在這段時間照顧兩個小朋友，之後又叫全場大合唱生日歌，預祝本月16日44歲的老婆生日快樂，隨後又唱出結婚時寫給老婆的英文歌，冧到楊洛婷大叫「I Love You！」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"謝寧前來捧場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/43de70b7c3727d2b4f5276bd0c4d582b/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0007.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        謝寧前來捧場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"馬浚偉前來捧場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b29e239c5e81fe5af474e5b497060b55/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0008.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬浚偉前來捧場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"主音黃天翱（Tim）的老婆楊洛婷與一對子女亦有到場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cc3dbfb2c99f8bb82f24eb7244e4e406/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0010.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        主音黃天翱（Tim）的老婆楊洛婷與一對子女亦有到場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"早前拍戲頸部受傷的魏浚笙亦有到場睇騷。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f5bae50e8b9f2e57e3951f99a5b2d9b/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0013.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        早前拍戲頸部受傷的魏浚笙亦有到場睇騷。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"被問到傷勢時，戴著口罩的他表示「好返好多」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1cdf8485d7b28e0880cf723811f29e9e/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0015.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        被問到傷勢時，戴著口罩的他表示「好返好多」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Tyson Yoshi以為只是來睇騷，沒想過在全場過萬名觀眾看著下與Christy嘴咀。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1d095054ce5020bd44b9c44c04f55a24/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0016_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Tyson Yoshi以為只是來睇騷，沒想過在全場過萬名觀眾看著下與Christy嘴咀。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Dear Jane成軍不經不覺已20年。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/74acfcd137e7ba3a49472e9490dfb6b3/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0034.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Dear Jane成軍不經不覺已20年。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"難得4位成員感情一直都很好。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5ed21a50c95e7531c7ec0d2cf781a2f0/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0039.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        難得4位成員感情一直都很好。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"在Tim彈結他時，兒子Tristan也走出坐位與台上爸爸對彈。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/45c6c2a01ee4e9df9de2aca82bbe4b72/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0041.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        在Tim彈結他時，兒子Tristan也走出坐位與台上爸爸對彈。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"在唱出《經過一些秋與冬》時，現場影著該MV系列的男主角胡卓希。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4793cb03090ea70de131e5a0eb07ad4f/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0043.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        在唱出《經過一些秋與冬》時，現場影著該MV系列的男主角胡卓希。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Tim也在演唱會上畀驚喜老婆，他先感激對方在這段時間照顧兩個小朋友，之後又叫全場大合唱生日歌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68d68500411452411c4336a8ec88f75c/2025-05/IMG-20250515-WA0046.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Tim也在演唱會上畀驚喜老婆，他先感激對方在這段時間照顧兩個小朋友，之後又叫全場大合唱生日歌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"4位成員傾力表演。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5eead6c5171804437e2366e768b48aea/2025-05/WhatsApp_2025-05-1500_17_33_b4440a7d.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        4位成員傾力表演。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"他們說不會哭，因為什麼都沒有的時候不哭，現在有更多的時候更不會哭。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/538cde148c9fd11ea3e93ccf2bb3dd28/2025-05/WhatsApp_2025-05-1500_17_34_2350f38d.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        他們說不會哭，因為什麼都沒有的時候不哭，現在有更多的時候更不會哭。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\" Encore時，Tim特別走到台邊跟歌迷握手\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f8eee5858d7e863e60c7552288082c04/2025-05/WhatsApp_2025-05-1500_17_34_6041e5f5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n         Encore時，Tim特別走到台邊跟歌迷握手\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>感謝歌迷20年支持</h2>\n<p>Encore時，Tim特別走到台邊跟歌迷握手，感謝他們廿年來支持，之後唱出《到此為止》及《無可避免》，Jackal感性地表示小時候夾Band覺得開心、滿足就足夠，以為熱血可贏到世界，憑音樂吸引很多人，但原來不簡單，用了20年才能吸引大家，又謂他們不會哭，因為什麼都沒有的時候不哭，現在有更多的時候更不會哭。最後Dear Jane憑歌寄意，再一次唱出《浮床》，為演唱會畫上句號。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
